Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:04:58.09,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你见到父亲了没？\N{\fs40}Have you seen your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.34,0:05:03.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你的小表妹刚刚失去母亲\N{\fs40}Your little cousins have lost their mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.34,0:05:05.01,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她们需要安慰\N{\fs40}They could use a kind word.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.10,0:05:06.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我也需要安慰\N{\fs40}I have an equal claim to sympathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.02,0:05:08.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 小杰 - 我们应该在赫伦堡\N{\fs40}-Jace. -We should be at Harrenhal,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.81,0:05:10.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,哀悼莱昂诺大人和哈尔温爵士\N{\fs40}mourning Lord Lyonel and Ser Harwin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.10,0:05:14.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这不妥当\N{\fs40}It would not be appropriate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.40,0:05:19.07,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,瓦列利安是我们的亲人 斯壮不是\N{\fs40}The Velaryons are our kin and the Strongs are not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.78,0:05:20.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,看着我\N{\fs40}Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.70,0:05:23.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你明白吗\N{\fs40}Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.85,0:05:53.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,手摇织机\N{\fs40}Hand turns loom;
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.52,0:05:55.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,绿线轴 黑线轴\N{\fs40}spool of green, spool of black;
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.52,0:05:57.86,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,龙之血肉\N{\fs40}dragons of flesh
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.94,0:06:00.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,编织龙之线\N{\fs40}weaving dragons of thread.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.57,0:06:03.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,手摇织机 绿线轴\N{\fs40}Hand turns loom; spool of green...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.95,0:06:07.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 我们一点都不像  - 她是我们的姐妹\N{\fs40}-We have nothing in common. -She's our sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.28,0:06:09.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 那你娶她 - 如果母亲让我们成婚\N{\fs40}-You marry her, then. -I would perform my duty,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.99,0:06:12.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 我自会履行职责 - “如果”\N{\fs40}-if mother had only betrothed us. - If only.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.71,0:06:14.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这会让家族强大\N{\fs40}It would strengthen the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.46,0:06:16.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,保持我们的瓦雷利亚血统纯正\N{\fs40}Keep our Valyrian blood pure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.21,0:06:18.80,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 她就是个白痴 - 她是你未来的王后\N{\fs40}-She's an idiot. -She's your future queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.21,0:06:23.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们确实有个\N{\fs40}We actually do have
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.30,0:06:25.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,共同之处\N{\fs40}one thing in common.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.97,0:06:29.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们都喜欢大长腿\N{\fs40}We both fancy creatures with very long legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.60,0:06:33.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,小妞儿！\N{\fs40}Wench!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.85,0:06:36.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 再来一杯！- 伊耿\N{\fs40}-Another! -Aegon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.85,0:06:39.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,……龙之血肉 编织龙之线\N{\fs40}...dragon's flesh, weaving dragons of thread.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.74,0:06:52.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,莱昂诺·斯壮的儿子从我们到这就一直盯着您 陛下\N{\fs40}Lyonel Strong's son's been staring at you since the moment we arrived, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.46,0:06:58.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,毫无避忌\N{\fs40}Unabashedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.50,0:07:02.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他只是在显摆 克里斯顿爵士\N{\fs40}It is only a look of pride, Ser Criston.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.96,0:07:05.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,拉里斯是新任赫伦堡伯爵\N{\fs40}Larys is the new Lord of Harrenhal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.38,0:07:42.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我的位子和高潮城\N{\fs40}Both my seat and High Tide
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.25,0:07:44.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,有一天都是你的 路斯里斯\N{\fs40}will be yours one day, Lucerys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.67,0:07:47.76,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,当然 你哥哥会当上国王\N{\fs40}Your brother will be king, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.76,0:07:51.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他会出席数不清的御前会议和庆典\N{\fs40}He'll sit on endless councils and ceremonies,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.76,0:07:53.97,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但做了潮汛之主 就能统治大海\N{\fs40}but Lord of the Tides rules the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.02,0:07:56.15,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\fs40}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.23,0:07:57.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我不想要\N{\fs40}I don't want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.23,0:08:03.15,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这是你生来就有的权利 小子\N{\fs40}It's your birthright, lad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.99,0:08:11.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果我当了潮头岛伯爵 就意味着所有人都死了\N{\fs40}If I'm the Lord of Driftmark, it means everyone's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.04,0:08:20.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 请您节哀 -谢谢 谢谢\N{\fs40}-I'm very sorry. -Thank you. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.61,0:08:45.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,外婆……\N{\fs40}Grandma...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.40,0:08:52.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我不想母亲去世\N{\fs40}I don't want Mother to be gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.61,0:10:08.15,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,把你主子找回来\N{\fs40}Retrieve your patron.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.65,0:10:12.78,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,哥哥\N{\fs40}Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.15,0:10:56.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你的女儿们和母亲长得一模一样\N{\fs40}Your girls are the very image of their mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.95,0:11:00.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,既是安慰 也是痛苦\N{\fs40}A comfort and an anguish,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.20,0:11:02.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我很清楚这滋味\N{\fs40}as I well remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.00,0:11:04.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,诸神有时很残忍\N{\fs40}The gods can be cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.21,0:11:09.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,看起来对你尤为残忍\N{\fs40}It seems they've been especially cruel to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.42,0:11:12.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs40}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.10,0:11:29.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你应该和我们一起回君临\N{\fs40}You should return with us to King's Landing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.90,0:11:31.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是时候回家了\N{\fs40}It's time that you came home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.61,0:11:33.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,潘托斯才是我的家……\N{\fs40}Pentos is my home...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.49,0:11:37.03,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 也是孩子们的家 - 戴蒙……\N{\fs40}-and that of my children. -Daemon...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.99,0:11:40.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我知道我们有过种种分歧\N{\fs40}I know we've had our differences,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.66,0:11:42.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但都过了这么久了 就随它们去吧\N{\fs40}but let them pass with the years.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.20,0:11:46.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果你想要\N{\fs40}There's a place for you in my court
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.33,0:11:47.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我就在朝中给你留个位子\N{\fs40}if that's something you should need.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.75,0:11:50.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我要⻗……我什么都不要\N{\fs40}I need... nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.05,0:12:01.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,弟弟\N{\fs40}Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.14,0:12:08.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,请节哀 王子殿下\N{\fs40}I'm sorry for your loss, my Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.23,0:12:12.90,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不管是多肥的水蛭 永远没有吸饱的时候\N{\fs40}No matter how fat the leech grows, it always wants for another meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.16,0:12:25.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,去睡觉\N{\fs40}Go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.41,0:12:27.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 但是 母亲 - 去睡觉\N{\fs40}-But, Mother-- -Go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.38,0:12:39.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我要去睡了 爱玛\N{\fs40}I'm going to bed, Aemma.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.76,0:12:44.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,需要我照看阿莉森王后吗 陛下？\N{\fs40}Shall I see after Queen Alicent, Your Grace?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.14,0:12:49.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不 哈罗德爵士\N{\fs40}No, Ser Harrold.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.81,0:12:51.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你去守夜班 克里斯顿爵士\N{\fs40}You have the night's watch, Ser Criston.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.98,0:12:55.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,遵命 队长大人\N{\fs40}Lord Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.93,0:13:30.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,弟弟？\N{\fs40}Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.02,0:13:37.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,滚回床上睡\N{\fs40}Get to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.96,0:14:41.55,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她想回家\N{\fs40}She wanted to come home
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.63,0:14:43.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但他拒绝了\N{\fs40}and he denied her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.47,0:14:47.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,戴蒙只是做了他觉得最好的选择\N{\fs40}Daemon did what he thought best.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.68,0:14:51.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,戴蒙只会做最利于自己的选择\N{\fs40}Daemon only ever does what is best for Daemon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.93,0:14:55.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,兰娜尔需要我们的学士\N{\fs40}Laena needed our maesters.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.40,0:15:02.99,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,潘托斯的医生和我们的学士\N{\fs40}The surgeons in Pentos are as well-trained
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.07,0:15:04.61,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一样医术高明\N{\fs40}as our maesters.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.57,0:15:13.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你这是因诸神之举迁怒他人\N{\fs40}You are looking to place blame for an act of the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.16,0:15:17.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,也许这正是诸神对我们的嘲弄……\N{\fs40}Mayhaps the gods have scorned us...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.83,0:15:21.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,因为我们贪得无厌 傲慢自大\N{\fs40}for our insatiable pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.80,0:15:29.76,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,王冠本是你的\N{\fs40}The crown was yours
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.85,0:15:34.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,却硬生生被大议会上那些蠢货夺走\N{\fs40}until those fools at the Great Council plucked it from your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.81,0:15:40.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,难道你的丈夫想替你夺回王冠 就如此不堪？\N{\fs40}Is it such a terrible thing for your husband to wish to win it back?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.52,0:15:43.65,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,今天晚上 就让我们抛开虚伪 坦诚相对\N{\fs40}Tonight of all nights, let us lay aside this falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.20,0:15:49.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,真正驱使你这么做的 不是为妻子伸张正义\N{\fs40}It is not justice for your wife that drives you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.32,0:15:50.99,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,而是实现自己的野心\N{\fs40}It is your own ambition.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.87,0:15:53.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是你对王座的野心\N{\fs40}'Tis desire for the throne,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.74,0:15:57.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果不是为了自己 就是为了你的子孙后代\N{\fs40}if not for yourself, then for the scions of your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.16,0:15:59.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我早就放弃对王位的念想了\N{\fs40}I gave up the idea of wearing a crown a generation ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.79,0:16:02.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是你 我的夫君 不愿放弃执念\N{\fs40}It is you, lord husband, who refuses to abandon this pursuit,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.00,0:16:05.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,即使它害了我们的孩子\N{\fs40}even now, at the cost of our children.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.02,0:16:23.36,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果不是为了家族传承\N{\fs40}What is this brief mortal life...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.61,0:16:26.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们这短暂平凡的一生又有什么意义？\N{\fs40}if not the pursuit of legacy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.49,0:16:29.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,传承后人 也许就是你一生所求 科利斯\N{\fs40}Legacy may be why you live your life, Corlys.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.79,0:16:44.34,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我想让兰娜尔的女儿贝妮拉继承潮头岛\N{\fs40}I want Driftmark to pass through Laena's line to Baela.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.38,0:16:48.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她是真正的瓦列利安血脉\N{\fs40}To true Velaryon blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.97,0:16:51.56,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,趁大家都在 现在就宣布此事\N{\fs40}Declare it now, while all are gathered here,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.64,0:16:54.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们可以说 这是为了纪念兰娜尔\N{\fs40}and we will say that is how we will honor Laena's memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.10,0:16:56.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就这么剥夺我们儿子的继承权？\N{\fs40}And disinherit our son?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.39,0:16:58.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他会成为王夫\N{\fs40}He will be the King Consort.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.68,0:17:00.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他的儿子有一天会登上铁王座\N{\fs40}His son will one day sit the Iron Throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.77,0:17:03.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你是要我对那两个被阴影笼罩的孩子\N{\fs40}You would have me cast an even darker shadow
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.52,0:17:05.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,落井下石\N{\fs40}over those little boys than already exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.48,0:17:06.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,现在没有旁人 夫君\N{\fs40}We are alone here, husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.82,0:17:09.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你可以说出真相 我们都心知肚明\N{\fs40}You can speak the plain truth as we both know it:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.12,0:17:19.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷妮拉的孩子不是你的血脉\N{\fs40}Rhaenyra's children are not of your blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.17,0:17:29.09,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但兰娜尔的孩子是\N{\fs40}But Laena's are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.59,0:17:34.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她们就是兰娜尔留给我们的传承\N{\fs40}They are her legacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.80,0:17:39.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,历史不会记得血脉\N{\fs40}History does not remember blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.06,0:17:45.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,只会铭记姓氏\N{\fs40}It remembers names.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.17,0:18:09.76,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,兰尼诺这几年都不大安分\N{\fs40}Laenor has been restless for years,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.84,0:18:14.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,到了现在 他更是指望不上\N{\fs40}but now, he will be useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.38,0:18:15.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,甚至更糟\N{\fs40}Or worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.26,0:18:21.01,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们的婚姻不过一场闹剧 我比谁都清楚\N{\fs40}I know better than anyone that our marriage is a farce.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.35,0:18:26.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但至少我还在努力维持体面\N{\fs40}But I at least make the effort to maintain appearances.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.40,0:18:28.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,因为你有更重的包袱\N{\fs40}You have more to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.23,0:18:33.78,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是啊 既然父亲立我为王储 这便是我的命运\N{\fs40}Yes, well, that has been my lot since my father named me heir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.49,0:18:38.03,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们确实曾经试着……\N{\fs40}We did try...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.74,0:18:41.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,去怀个孩子\N{\fs40}to conceive a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.20,0:18:45.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们尽了最大努力去履行自己的责任\N{\fs40}We performed our duty as best we could.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.04,0:18:49.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但一切都是徒劳\N{\fs40}But to no avail.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.80,0:18:58.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,整个过程毫无乐趣\N{\fs40}There was no joy in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.77,0:19:04.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但我在其他地方找到了乐趣\N{\fs40}I found that elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.77,0:19:09.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,被人渴望的感觉真不错\N{\fs40}It felt good to be desired.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.86,0:19:15.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我知道哈尔温爵士对你非常……\N{\fs40}I understand Ser Harwin was quite...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.66,0:19:19.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,忠诚\N{\fs40}devoted to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.62,0:19:23.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,没错 他的确如此\N{\fs40}Yes, he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.96,0:19:26.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我也很信任他\N{\fs40}And I trusted him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.71,0:19:34.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我应该阻止哈尔温爵士回到河间地\N{\fs40}Should've forbidden Ser Harwin from returning to the Riverlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.63,0:19:39.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,伊耿征服之后赫伦堡就流传着可怕的诅咒 现在看来还是那么强大\N{\fs40}Harren's curse is said to be as strong now as it was after the Conquest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.01,0:19:41.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那不过是个鬼故事\N{\fs40}That's a ghost story,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.51,0:19:44.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,奥托爵士和王后乐于拿它大做文章\N{\fs40}one Ser Otto and the Queen would gladly exploit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.98,0:19:48.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我不相信阿莉森会这么冷血地杀人\N{\fs40}I do not believe Alicent capable of cold murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.73,0:19:55.27,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们每个人都可能堕落\N{\fs40}Each of us is capable of depravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.90,0:19:58.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,程度远超你的想象\N{\fs40}And more than you would believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.33,0:20:04.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果说的是你 那我确实相信\N{\fs40}I believe it of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.58,0:20:08.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果你想指责我堕落了\N{\fs40}If you're accusing me of some depravity,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.25,0:20:10.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不妨把话说明白点\N{\fs40}you'll need to be more specific.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.46,0:20:14.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我一直孤身一人\N{\fs40}I've been alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.55,0:20:17.72,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 你抛弃了我  - 我放过了你\N{\fs40}-You abandoned me. -I spared you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.80,0:20:20.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 那时你还是个孩子 - 没错\N{\fs40}-You were a child. -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.47,0:20:22.22,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,没错 那时我还是个孩子\N{\fs40}Yes, I was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.30,0:20:24.84,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,看看没有你 我的人生变成了什么样子\N{\fs40}And look at what my life became without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.73,0:20:28.61,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,可笑的悲剧\N{\fs40}Droll tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.69,0:20:31.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,反过来说 你以为我的人生又过成了什么样？\N{\fs40}And I wonder what you think of mine by comparison?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.40,0:20:32.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我对你这几年一无所知\N{\fs40}I know little of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.82,0:20:40.36,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你爱过她吗？\N{\fs40}Did you love her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.03,0:20:44.78,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们很幸福\N{\fs40}We were happy enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.33,0:20:48.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,嗯 那就算很了不起了\N{\fs40}Well, that in itself is a great achievement.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.75,0:20:56.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 我很抱歉 - 不必\N{\fs40}-I am sorry. -Don't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.80,0:21:01.34,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,至少我还能哀悼逝去的爱人\N{\fs40}I am at least allowed to mourn my losses.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.83,0:21:33.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷妮拉\N{\fs40}Rhaenyra.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.46,0:21:40.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我不再是个孩子了\N{\fs40}I'm no longer a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.53,0:22:02.07,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我想要你\N{\fs40}I want you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.84,0:25:05.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,操\N{\fs40}Fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.30,0:26:36.22,Subtitle_Valyrian_NOen,,0,0,0,,乖！\N{\fs40}Dohaerās!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.93,0:26:40.18,Subtitle_Valyrian_NOen,,0,0,0,,乖 瓦格哈尔！冷静！\N{\fs40}Dohaerās, Vhagar! Lykirī!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.47,0:26:42.81,Subtitle_Valyrian_NOen,,0,0,0,,冷静！\N{\fs40}Lykirī!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.81,0:26:48.94,Subtitle_Valyrian_NOen,,0,0,0,,冷静\N{\fs40}Lykirī.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.74,0:27:38.87,Subtitle_Valyrian_NOen,,0,0,0,,飞！\N{\fs40}Sōvēs!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.12,0:27:45.67,Subtitle_Valyrian_NOen,,0,0,0,,乖 瓦格哈尔！飞！\N{\fs40}Dohaerās, Vhagar! Sōvēs!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.27,0:29:36.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,哇！\N{\fs40}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.51,0:30:02.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,小杰 小杰\N{\fs40}Jace, Jace.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.47,0:30:05.01,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,小杰 醒醒 醒醒\N{\fs40}Jace, wake up. Wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.85,0:30:09.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 有人偷走了瓦格哈尔 - 什么？\N{\fs40}-Someone stole Vhagar. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.79,0:30:30.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那是谁？\N{\fs40}Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.40,0:30:57.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,小杰 我们怎么办？\N{\fs40}Jace, what are we doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.65,0:30:59.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 就是他 - 是我没错\N{\fs40}-It's him. -It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.82,0:31:02.99,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 瓦格哈尔是我妈妈的龙 - 你妈妈已经死了\N{\fs40}-Vhagar is my mother's dragon. -Your mother's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.07,0:31:05.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 瓦格哈尔现在有新骑手了 - 她是属于我的\N{\fs40}-And Vhagar has a new rider now. -She was mine to claim.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.53,0:31:07.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那你就该早点去驯服她\N{\fs40}Then you should've claimed her!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.32,0:31:09.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,也许你的表兄弟们会帮你找一头猪骑\N{\fs40}Maybe your cousins can find you a pig to ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.62,0:31:10.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那很适合你\N{\fs40}It would suit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.83,0:31:18.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你再敢过来 我就拿你喂我的龙！\N{\fs40}Come at me again and I'll feed you to my dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.83,0:31:54.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你会像你父亲一样在火焰中尖叫着死去！\N{\fs40}You will die screaming in flames just as your father did!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.29,0:31:55.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,野种\N{\fs40}Bastards.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.37,0:31:57.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我父亲还活着\N{\fs40}My father's still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.12,0:32:00.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他还不知道 是吗 斯壮大人？\N{\fs40}He doesn't know, does he, Lord Strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.30,0:32:04.22,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,小杰！\N{\fs40}Jace!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.44,0:32:25.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,马上住手！\N{\fs40}Cease this at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.28,0:32:28.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,让开！\N{\fs40}Get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.07,0:32:33.99,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,王子殿下 王子殿下 让我看看\N{\fs40}My Prince, my Prince. Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.71,0:32:39.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,诸神保佑\N{\fs40}Gods be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.96,0:32:43.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你怎么能让这样的事情发生？\N{\fs40}How could you allow such a thing to happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.80,0:32:47.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,给我查个清楚\N{\fs40}I will have answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.47,0:32:50.01,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,王子们应该是在睡觉的 国王陛下\N{\fs40}The princes were supposed to be abed, My King.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.72,0:32:52.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是谁在值夜？\N{\fs40}Who had the watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.89,0:32:55.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,陛下 小王子受到了表亲们的攻击\N{\fs40}Young prince was attacked by his own cousins, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.60,0:32:59.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你们曾发誓要保护捍卫我的血脉！\N{\fs40}You swore oaths to protect and defend my blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.81,0:33:01.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉 陛下\N{\fs40}I'm very sorry, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.48,0:33:03.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,御林铁卫从来没试过 要阻止王子伤害王子\N{\fs40}The Kingsguard has never had to defend princes from princes,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.77,0:33:05.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 陛下 - 这不是我要的答复！\N{\fs40}-Your Grace. -That is no answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.82,0:33:08.03,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,会痊愈的 对吗 学士？\N{\fs40}It will heal, will it not, maester?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.20,0:33:11.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,血肉会愈合\N{\fs40}The flesh will heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.66,0:33:16.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但是眼睛保不住了 王后陛下\N{\fs40}But the eye is lost, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.25,0:33:21.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 当时你在哪里？ - 我吗？\N{\fs40}-Where were you? -Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.50,0:33:23.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 打我干什么？ - 弟弟被人欺负的时候\N{\fs40}-What was that for? -That was nothing compared to
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.62,0:33:25.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你却喝个烂醉如泥\N{\fs40}the abuse your brother suffered
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.21,0:33:27.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这一巴掌算得了什么 你这个傻瓜\N{\fs40}while you were drowning in your cups, you fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.26,0:33:29.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事？\N{\fs40}What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.72,0:33:32.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,贝妮拉 雷妮亚 发生了什么？\N{\fs40}Baela, Rhaena! What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.18,0:33:33.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,发生了什么？\N{\fs40}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.27,0:33:39.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,小杰？\N{\fs40}Jace?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.14,0:33:41.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,小路！\N{\fs40}Luke!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.15,0:33:45.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,让我看看 让我看看\N{\fs40}Show me. Show me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.48,0:33:47.11,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 谁干的？ - 他们打我！\N{\fs40}-Who did this? -They attacked me!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.19,0:33:49.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 他打了贝妮拉！ - 他打断了小路的鼻子！\N{\fs40}-He attacked Baela! -He broke Luke's nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.70,0:33:56.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他偷了我妈妈的龙！\N{\fs40}He stole my mother's dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.95,0:33:58.99,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 够了 - 他还想杀了小杰！\N{\fs40}-Enough. -He was gonna kill Jace!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.08,0:34:00.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 我什么也没做！ - 够了——\N{\fs40}-I didn't do anything! -Enough--
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.20,0:34:01.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,应该听我儿子怎么说！\N{\fs40}It should be my son telling the tale!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.62,0:34:03.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 他叫我们—— - 安静！\N{\fs40}-He called us-- - Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.30,0:34:09.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他叫我们野种\N{\fs40}He called us bastards.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.76,0:34:17.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,伊蒙德……\N{\fs40}Aemond...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.72,0:34:19.56,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我要知道事情的真相\N{\fs40}I will have the truth of what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.68,0:34:23.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 现在就说 - 还有什么可问的？\N{\fs40}-Now. -What else is there to hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.77,0:34:25.86,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你儿子残了 她儿子干的\N{\fs40}Your son has been maimed. Her son is responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.94,0:34:28.11,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 这是一场令人遗憾的意外 - 意外?\N{\fs40}-It was a regrettable accident. -Accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.19,0:34:30.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,路斯里斯王子带了一把匕首来伏击\N{\fs40}The Prince Lucerys brought a blade to the ambush.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.49,0:34:32.07,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他想要杀了我儿子\N{\fs40}He meant to kill my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.15,0:34:34.65,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是我的儿子们受到攻击\N{\fs40}It was my sons who were attacked
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.74,0:34:37.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们不得不自卫\N{\fs40}and forced to defend themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.45,0:34:40.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们遭受了恶毒的侮辱\N{\fs40}Vile insults were levied against them.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.37,0:34:41.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,什么侮辱？\N{\fs40}What insults?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.63,0:34:49.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,有人胆敢公开质疑我儿子们的正统血脉\N{\fs40}The legitimacy of my sons' birth was put loudly to question.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.13,0:34:51.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 什么？ - 他叫我们野种\N{\fs40}-What? -He called us bastards.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.72,0:35:00.97,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,陛下 我的儿子们是铁王座的顺位继承人\N{\fs40}My sons are in line to inherit the Iron Throne, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.06,0:35:03.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这是最为严重的叛国罪行\N{\fs40}This is the highest of treasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.77,0:35:06.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,伊蒙德王子必须受到严厉讯问\N{\fs40}Prince Aemond must be sharply questioned
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.81,0:35:09.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,让他交代到底是从哪里听到的这些谣言\N{\fs40}so we might learn where he heard such slanders.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.23,0:35:12.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就因为一句侮辱的话？\N{\fs40}Over an insult?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.78,0:35:16.07,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我的儿子失去了一只眼睛\N{\fs40}My son has lost an eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.66,0:35:21.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,告诉我 孩子 你从哪里听来这谣言的？\N{\fs40}You tell me, boy. Where did you hear this lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.70,0:35:23.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,所谓侮辱不过是训练场上打闹喊话\N{\fs40}The insult was training yard bluster.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.37,0:35:25.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 男孩子在一起都这样 没什么 - 伊蒙德……\N{\fs40}-The lot of boys. It was nothing. -Aemond...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.83,0:35:27.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我在问你问题\N{\fs40}I asked you a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.55,0:35:33.55,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我想知道 孩子们的父亲兰尼诺爵士去哪儿了\N{\fs40}Where is Ser Laenor, I wonder? The boys' father?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.63,0:35:35.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,对于这件事 也许他有话要说\N{\fs40}Perhaps he might have something to say in the matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.76,0:35:37.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是啊 兰尼诺爵士呢\N{\fs40}Yes. Where is Ser Laenor?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.18,0:35:41.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我不知道 陛下 我…… 睡不着\N{\fs40}I do not know, Your Grace. I... could not find sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.89,0:35:43.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就出门散心了\N{\fs40}I had gone out to walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.85,0:35:46.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,想必是跟他的小侍从们找乐子去了\N{\fs40}Entertaining his young squires, I would venture.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.19,0:35:51.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,伊蒙德\N{\fs40}Aemond...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.86,0:35:53.99,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,看着我\N{\fs40}look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.40,0:35:58.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你的国王命令你必须回答\N{\fs40}Your king demands an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.53,0:36:00.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,谁告诉你的这个谣言？\N{\fs40}Who spoke these lies to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.13,0:36:19.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,伊耿说的\N{\fs40}It was Aegon.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.22,0:36:23.22,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我？\N{\fs40}Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.89,0:36:28.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那你呢 小子？\N{\fs40}And you, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.06,0:36:33.61,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你又是从哪听到的这些诽谤？\N{\fs40}Where did you hear such calumnies?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.44,0:36:37.99,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,伊耿！你给我说实话\N{\fs40}Aegon! Tell me the truth of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.78,0:36:42.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们都知道 父亲\N{\fs40}We know, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.08,0:36:46.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,大家都知道\N{\fs40}Everyone knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.75,0:36:49.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,瞧他们那样\N{\fs40}Just look at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.22,0:37:09.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们必须停止这样无休无止地内斗！\N{\fs40}This interminable infighting must cease!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.48,0:37:10.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,所有人都给我住手！\N{\fs40}All of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.48,0:37:15.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们是一家人！\N{\fs40}We are family!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.03,0:37:23.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,现在你们各自道歉 向对方表达善意\N{\fs40}Now make your apologies and show good will to one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.12,0:37:28.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你们的父亲 祖父和国王命令你们\N{\fs40}Your father, your grandsire, your king demands it!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.30,0:37:44.84,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这就够了吗\N{\fs40}That is insufficient.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.85,0:37:50.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,伊蒙德受到了永久伤害 我的国王陛下\N{\fs40}Aemond has been damaged, permanently, My King.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.10,0:37:51.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,“善意”无法让他完好如初\N{\fs40}"Good will" cannot make him whole.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.73,0:37:55.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我很清楚 阿莉森 我也没法让他的眼睛复原\N{\fs40}I know, Alicent, but I cannot restore his eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.48,0:37:57.15,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是啊 因为被人夺走了\N{\fs40}No, because it's been taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.23,0:38:00.78,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 那你想让我怎么办？ - 血债必须血偿\N{\fs40}-What would you have me do? -There is a debt to be paid.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.20,0:38:08.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,让她儿子赔我们一只眼睛\N{\fs40}I shall have one of her son's eyes in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.70,0:38:13.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 我亲爱的妻子 - 他是你的儿子 韦赛里斯\N{\fs40}-My dear wife. -He is your son, Viserys.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.17,0:38:14.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你的血脉\N{\fs40}Your blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.67,0:38:16.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,请不要\N{\fs40}Do not...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.13,0:38:19.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,让愤怒左右你的判断\N{\fs40}allow your temper to guide your judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.22,0:38:28.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,要是国王不主持公道 王后自会主持\N{\fs40}If the King will not seek justice, the Queen will.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.14,0:38:29.27,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,克里斯顿爵士……\N{\fs40}Ser Criston...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.68,0:38:32.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,给我挖了路斯里斯·瓦列利安的眼睛\N{\fs40}bring me the eye of Lucerys Velaryon.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.81,0:38:34.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 母亲！ - 阿莉森\N{\fs40}-Mother! -Alicent.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.06,0:38:37.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他可以选择留下哪只 我儿子可没享受到这等福利\N{\fs40}He can choose which eye to keep, a privilege he did not grant my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.82,0:38:39.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你不能这么做\N{\fs40}You will do no such thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.32,0:38:41.86,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 都不许动 - 不行 你向我宣誓过\N{\fs40}-Stay your hand. -No, you are sworn to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.37,0:38:48.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我发誓会护您周全 王后陛下\N{\fs40}As your protector, my Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.54,0:38:56.55,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,阿莉森 这件事…… 到此为止\N{\fs40}Alicent, this matter... is finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.63,0:38:58.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,听懂了吗？\N{\fs40}Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.51,0:39:11.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,所有人都给我记住\N{\fs40}And let it be known:
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.22,0:39:13.22,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,倘若有任何人胆敢对雷妮拉公主之子的血统\N{\fs40}anyone whose tongue dares to question the birth
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.31,0:39:15.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,提出质疑 散布谣言\N{\fs40}of Princess Rhaenyra's sons
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.56,0:39:17.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我会割了你们的舌头\N{\fs40}should have it removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.52,0:39:22.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,谢谢您 父亲\N{\fs40}Thank you, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.95,0:39:34.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 陛下 - 阿莉森！回到你的国王身边来！\N{\fs40}-Your Grace. -Alicent! Stay with the King!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.96,0:39:36.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不要再往前走了！\N{\fs40}Hold your approach!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.71,0:39:38.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 别过去 克里斯顿爵士！ - 阿莉森！\N{\fs40}-Do not, Ser Criston! -Alicent!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.50,0:39:40.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,别过去 克里斯顿爵士！\N{\fs40}Do not, Ser Criston!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.25,0:39:41.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,阿莉森！\N{\fs40}Alicent!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.25,0:39:43.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不！\N{\fs40}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.38,0:39:46.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你不许动 科尔！\N{\fs40}Stay your hand, Cole!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.68,0:39:49.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你做得太过火了\N{\fs40}You've gone too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.26,0:39:50.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我？\N{\fs40}I?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.68,0:39:52.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,除了满足他人对我的要求和期待 我又做了什么过火的事？\N{\fs40}What have I done but what was expected of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.10,0:39:57.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一直以来我都在维护着我们的王国 家庭和律法\N{\fs40}Forever upholding the kingdom, the family, the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.27,0:40:02.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 你却藐视一切 随心所欲 - 阿莉森 放开她！\N{\fs40}-While you flout all to do as you please. -Alicent, let her go!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.40,0:40:04.90,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你的责任呢？你的牺牲呢？\N{\fs40}Where is duty? Where is sacrifice?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.99,0:40:06.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一次次被你那双美丽的脚肆意践踏\N{\fs40}It's trampled under your pretty foot again.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.82,0:40:08.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,把刀子放下 阿莉森\N{\fs40}Release the blade, Alicent.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.16,0:40:11.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,现在你害我儿子少了一只眼睛\N{\fs40}And now you take my son's eye,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.41,0:40:13.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,即便这样 你还是这么理直气壮\N{\fs40}and to even that, you feel entitled.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.08,0:40:15.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你不累吗？\N{\fs40}Exhausting, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.20,0:40:18.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,总是躲藏在公正得体的长袍之下\N{\fs40}Hiding beneath the cloak of your own righteousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.21,0:40:22.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,现在大家都见识到你这副面孔了\N{\fs40}But now they see you as you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.96,0:41:01.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不用为我伤心 母亲\N{\fs40}Do not mourn me, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.08,0:41:03.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这是一桩公平的交易\N{\fs40}It was a fair exchange.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.00,0:41:06.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我虽然少了只眼睛\N{\fs40}I may have lost an eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.47,0:41:10.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但得到了一条龙\N{\fs40}but I gained a dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.77,0:41:20.90,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,相关事件就到此为止\N{\fs40}This proceeding is at an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.97,0:42:00.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,首相大人求见 陛下\N{\fs40}The Hand, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.74,0:42:19.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,有话说话\N{\fs40}Say your piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.70,0:42:21.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,事到如今还能说什么呢？\N{\fs40}Now, what piece is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.83,0:42:27.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我刚刚的所作所为……\N{\fs40}I've conducted myself in a manner...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.71,0:42:29.84,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,即便不以王后的标准看待\N{\fs40}unbefitting my station.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.38,0:42:32.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,依然有失体面\N{\fs40}Or any other.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.18,0:42:37.72,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我失去了理智……\N{\fs40}I lost composure...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.77,0:42:41.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,袭击了公主\N{\fs40}assaulted the Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.64,0:42:47.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,大家已经在传闲话 怀疑我是不是疯了\N{\fs40}Already the word is spreading, the gossip speculating that I've gone mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.90,0:42:50.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你说得都对\N{\fs40}All true.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.57,0:42:52.11,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我让自己丢脸了\N{\fs40}I disgraced myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.32,0:42:57.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我让丈夫永远都会偏向她女儿那边\N{\fs40}And ensured my husband's favor will forever rest on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.45,0:43:00.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但是呢……\N{\fs40}And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.54,0:43:05.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我从没见过这样的你 我的女儿\N{\fs40}I've never seen that side of you, my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.25,0:43:09.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我一度怀疑你没有这样的一面\N{\fs40}I even doubted its existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.05,0:43:13.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 丑恶的一面 我很后悔 - 我们本来就在玩一场丑恶的游戏\N{\fs40}-It was an ugly thing. I regret it. -We play an ugly game.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.47,0:43:16.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如今 我这辈子第一次\N{\fs40}And now, for the first time,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.93,0:43:20.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,看到了你想赢的决心\N{\fs40}I see that you have the determination to win it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.10,0:43:27.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 雷妮拉—— - 你也看清她的为人了\N{\fs40}-Rhaenyra-- -You see her for what she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.31,0:43:30.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,瞧瞧国王的偏执把她惯成什么样子\N{\fs40}What the King's stubbornness has wrought.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.40,0:43:36.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 他会跟我说些什么？ - 他会原谅你的\N{\fs40}-What will he say to me? -He'll forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.99,0:43:40.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不然他还能做什么\N{\fs40}What else can he do?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.83,0:43:44.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,快去找他吧 显出悔恨的样子\N{\fs40}Now go to him, be penitent,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.58,0:43:47.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,为你儿子的伤辩解一番\N{\fs40}plead the injury to your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.33,0:43:49.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,控制好情绪不要激动\N{\fs40}Keep a grip on your passions.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.25,0:43:54.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我向你保证 你我联手一定能赢得这场游戏\N{\fs40}And I promise you, in time, you and I together will prevail.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.59,0:43:59.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,伊蒙德撒的野\N{\fs40}What that rogue Aemond has done
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.72,0:44:02.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,为我们赢得了瓦格哈尔\N{\fs40}in winning Vhagar to our side.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.22,0:44:05.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,孩子说得对\N{\fs40}The boy was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.89,0:44:09.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这比他付出的代价值一千倍\N{\fs40}It's worth a thousand times the price he paid.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.34,0:44:39.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,肯定要留疤 但伤口会愈合的\N{\fs40}You will scar, but the wound will heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.84,0:44:43.34,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,瓦雷利亚钢的创口都很平整\N{\fs40}Valyrian steel cuts clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.90,0:44:51.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,诸神啊\N{\fs40}Gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.98,0:44:55.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,大家都还好么？\N{\fs40}Is everyone all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.86,0:44:57.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,最糟糕的伤是断了鼻子\N{\fs40}A broken nose is the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.61,0:44:58.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 学士\N{\fs40}Thank you, maester.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.61,0:45:00.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,先退下吧\N{\fs40}Leave us.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.95,0:45:06.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你俩也出去\N{\fs40}You as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.62,0:45:09.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,今天惹的祸已经够多了\N{\fs40}You've already found enough trouble today.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.54,0:45:10.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,好的 母亲\N{\fs40}Yes, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.67,0:45:20.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我应该在场的\N{\fs40}I should've been there.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.38,0:45:22.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不如把这句话当咱们的族语吧\N{\fs40}Those should be our house words.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.39,0:45:28.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我曾和那么多可怕的敌人战斗\N{\fs40}I have fought dreadful enemies,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.18,0:45:30.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,却没能保护好自己的妹妹\N{\fs40}but I could not defend my dear sister
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.89,0:45:33.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她远离家乡 吃了那么多苦\N{\fs40}far from home and in agony.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.52,0:45:37.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 我也没能保护好你 - 坐吧\N{\fs40}-I could not defend you. -Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.20,0:45:50.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,伊蒙德叫我们的儿子野种\N{\fs40}Aemond called our sons bastards.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.38,0:45:59.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我让你失望了 雷妮拉\N{\fs40}I have failed you, Rhaenyra.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.05,0:46:01.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们的婚姻\N{\fs40}Our marriage...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.89,0:46:04.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我尽力了\N{\fs40}I tried.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.39,0:46:07.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们的儿子\N{\fs40}Our boys...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.43,0:46:10.97,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 我真的爱他们  - 我知道\N{\fs40}-I do love them. -I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.06,0:46:12.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,真的很爱\N{\fs40}Deeply.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.36,0:46:18.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但是 也许\N{\fs40}But I have not, mayhaps...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.90,0:46:21.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,还是爱得不够吧\N{\fs40}loved them enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.20,0:46:29.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们同床共枕那几次\N{\fs40}I had hoped to bear your children.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.50,0:46:33.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我希望能怀上你的孩子\N{\fs40}The few times we lay together.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.21,0:46:39.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果成功 可能一切就都不同了\N{\fs40}Things might've been different.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.72,0:46:45.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我痛恨诸神让我成为这个样子\N{\fs40}I hate the gods for making me as they did.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.01,0:46:48.55,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我不觉得\N{\fs40}I do not.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.35,0:46:50.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你高贵正直\N{\fs40}You are an honorable man
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.02,0:46:53.56,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,心地善良\N{\fs40}with a good heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.15,0:46:57.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这很难得\N{\fs40}It's a rare thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.82,0:47:05.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,多年以前我们就达成了协议\N{\fs40}We made an arrangement all those years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.28,0:47:07.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,履行职责的同时\N{\fs40}to do our duty and...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.91,0:47:10.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不耽误彼此寻找快乐\N{\fs40}yet explore happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.75,0:47:20.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但有些时候\N{\fs40}But there are times
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.25,0:47:23.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我觉得职责与快乐无法兼顾\N{\fs40}I think when these things cannot mutually exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.47,0:47:30.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,卡尔爵士很快就会重返石阶列岛的战场\N{\fs40}Ser Qarl will return soon to the fighting in the Stepstones.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.18,0:47:34.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但我会捡起承诺 留在你身边\N{\fs40}But I recommit myself to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.14,0:47:40.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,巩固我们的家族 为你来日登基做好准备\N{\fs40}And to strengthening our house as we prepare you for your ascension.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.52,0:47:43.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,把我们的儿子养育成为合格的王子\N{\fs40}I will raise our sons to be princes of the realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.78,0:47:46.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 兰尼诺   - 你值得比我更好的\N{\fs40}-Laenor-- -You deserve better than what I have been.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.07,0:47:50.99,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你需要丈夫在身边\N{\fs40}You deserve a husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.31,0:48:14.15,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我已经让人在船上备好了酒\N{\fs40}I've asked them to have wine ready for you on the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.22,0:48:15.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,喝了睡个好觉\N{\fs40}To help you sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.94,0:48:25.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉\N{\fs40}I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.49,0:48:29.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,韦赛里斯\N{\fs40}Viserys...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.74,0:48:31.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这事不必再提了\N{\fs40}We will speak no more of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.78,0:49:49.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,火 是如此神奇的力量\N{\fs40}Fire is such strange power.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.32,0:49:57.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,坦格利安家族拥有的一切都归功于火\N{\fs40}Everything that House Targaryen possesses is owed to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.87,0:50:02.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但火也让我们两人痛失所爱\N{\fs40}Yet it has cost us both what we loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.08,0:50:05.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,恐怕瓦列利安家族早就明白\N{\fs40}Perhaps the Velaryons knew the truth of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.88,0:50:07.80,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,大海才是更好的盟友\N{\fs40}The sea is the better ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.17,0:50:11.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,烈火是牢笼\N{\fs40}Fire is a prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.38,0:50:13.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,大海赐予了解脱\N{\fs40}The sea offers an escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.15,0:50:25.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这是正义的扭曲\N{\fs40}A perversion of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.48,0:50:28.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,小王子 含冤受辱\N{\fs40}The young prince...defiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.11,0:50:31.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,此等暴行 骇人听闻\N{\fs40}An outrage.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.41,0:50:34.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fs40}Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.29,0:50:42.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果您需要以眼还眼 我愿随时效劳\N{\fs40}If it's an eye you want to balance the scales, I am your servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.79,0:50:49.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,倒也不必如此\N{\fs40}That will not be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.55,0:50:54.84,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但你的忠诚我铭记于心\N{\fs40}But your devotion has not gone unnoticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.51,0:50:58.55,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,危险的时代已经到来\N{\fs40}These are dangerous times.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.19,0:51:06.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,迟早有一天 我需要一个你这样的朋友\N{\fs40}The day will doubtless come when I require such a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.73,0:51:11.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,既有高超技艺 又能独当一面\N{\fs40}With not only skill but discretion as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.15,0:51:17.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,随时等候您的差遣 王后陛下\N{\fs40}I shall await your call, my Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.38,0:51:35.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我需要你 叔叔\N{\fs40}I need you, Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.74,0:52:40.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,兰尼诺不死 我们没法结婚\N{\fs40}We could not marry unless Laenor were dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.08,0:52:47.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fs40}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.22,0:53:04.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我听说你在石阶列岛立了赫赫战功\N{\fs40}I've heard about your exploits in the Stepstones,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.85,0:53:06.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,卡尔爵士\N{\fs40}Ser Qarl.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.81,0:53:09.65,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,人们称道你是个身手不凡的骑士\N{\fs40}Said to be a knight of remarkable skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.73,0:53:11.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,过奖了 大人\N{\fs40}You flatter me, m'lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.52,0:53:13.61,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但可惜啊 平民出身\N{\fs40}But alas, common-born.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.32,0:53:17.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一个无产骑士 却有着领主的品味\N{\fs40}You're a landless knight with a lord's taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.99,0:53:19.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,兰尼诺爵士对我非常慷慨\N{\fs40}Ser Laenor's been kind to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.41,0:53:22.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你知道吗\N{\fs40}Do you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.33,0:53:28.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,狭海对面有些地方\N{\fs40}there are places across the Narrow Sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.12,0:53:32.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,没人会在意一个人的名字\N{\fs40}where it doesn't matter what a man's name is?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.00,0:53:35.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,只在乎他兜里有多少金子\N{\fs40}Only how much gold he possesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.09,0:53:41.01,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,大人 您想让我做什么\N{\fs40}What are you asking of me, m'lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.55,0:53:44.09,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一场干脆利落的死亡\N{\fs40}A quick death.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.97,0:53:46.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,记得留个见证人\N{\fs40}One with witnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.44,0:53:56.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我不会做一个\N{\fs40}I will not be a tyrant.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.40,0:53:59.99,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,依靠恐怖统治的暴君\N{\fs40}And rule through terror.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.95,0:54:02.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,只会散播恐怖才叫暴君\N{\fs40}A tyrant rules only through terror.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.62,0:54:12.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但无人惧怕的君王 也不会拥有权力\N{\fs40}If the King isn't feared, he is powerless.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.25,0:54:16.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果你想做一个强大的女王 固然需要臣民爱戴你崇敬你\N{\fs40}If you are to be a strong queen, you must cultivate love and respect, yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.38,0:54:19.09,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但也必须让他们畏惧你\N{\fs40}but your subjects must fear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.17,0:54:20.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,谁让你进来的？\N{\fs40}Who let you in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.39,0:54:26.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你到我父亲的大厅来做什么？\N{\fs40}Why are you in my father's hall?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.69,0:54:33.61,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你一直都看不起我\N{\fs40}You have always looked down on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.77,0:54:37.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我确实爱兰尼诺\N{\fs40}I do love Laenor.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.15,0:54:39.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那就赐他慈悲\N{\fs40}Then grant him this kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.24,0:54:41.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,让他解脱\N{\fs40}Set him free.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.49,0:54:43.03,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你以为自己是什么身份\N{\fs40}You forget yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.28,0:54:47.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,大人 求您不要！\N{\fs40}My lord. Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.46,0:54:54.55,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我去叫守卫！\N{\fs40}I'll alert the guards!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.59,0:55:07.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这样会让科利斯大人和雷妮丝公主\N{\fs40}This will cost Lord Corlys and Princess Rhaenys
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.14,0:55:09.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,失去他们现在唯一的孩子\N{\fs40}their only remaining child.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.23,0:55:15.36,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,王国上下会议论纷纷 认为我是那个幕后黑手\N{\fs40}And the realm will whisper that I was somehow responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.19,0:55:20.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不！\N{\fs40}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.03,0:55:22.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,让他们议论\N{\fs40}Let them whisper.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.49,0:55:24.03,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不！\N{\fs40}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.53,0:55:27.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你们是怎么当的守卫？\N{\fs40}How did you let this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.95,0:55:29.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我自家厅堂也他妈能出这种事？\N{\fs40}In my fucking hall?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.99,0:55:31.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,告诉我！\N{\fs40}Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.29,0:55:34.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们知道真相 敌人蒙在鼓里\N{\fs40}We will know the truth of it and our enemies won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.46,0:55:38.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们会害怕 畏惧我们的能耐\N{\fs40}They will fear what else we might be capable of.
