Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.60,0:02:15.31,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,今日我们齐聚海中宝座\N{\fs40}Tubī Velario Lentro Ābrāzme
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.40,0:02:19.61,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,安葬瓦列利安家族的兰娜尔夫人\N{\fs40}Laene iēdrarta mōrqittot,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.69,0:02:26.49,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,到永恒水域 人鱼王的领地\N{\fs40}māzīlarē tubirri Elēdrion ziry umīsilza luo dāriot,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.57,0:02:30.50,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,从此人鱼王会永远守护她\N{\fs40}hannagon Embrurliot gierūlti.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.54,0:02:36.21,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,她将最后一次入海远航\N{\fs40}Solion tolijor zijosy pradarose,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.29,0:02:43.30,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,兰娜尔夫人在岸上留下了两位亲生女儿\N{\fs40}Ābrāzma Laena rāeniot hen eglio ilvot lanto taloti hembis.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.22,0:02:51.85,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,尽管她们的母亲不再归航\N{\fs40}Pōja muña hen zȳho solio āmāzīlus daor,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.93,0:02:55.73,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,她们依然血脉相连\N{\fs40}yn ānogrosa gierī ozletaksi humbilza.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.69,0:03:02.11,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,海盐淌过瓦列利安的血脉\N{\fs40}Velario ānogro rȳ lopor ojāris.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.61,0:03:06.82,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,我们血脉浓稠\N{\fs40}Īlvon qumblī iāris.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.82,0:03:11.33,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,我们血脉纯正\N{\fs40}Īlvon drējī iāris.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.12,0:03:18.88,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,而我们的血脉绝不可淡薄\N{\fs40}Se dōrī vajiñagon īlvon bēvilis.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.81,0:03:33.98,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,我温婉的侄女\N{\fs40}Talus mandus ñuhus.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.06,0:03:39.48,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,愿海风如你脊背般坚强\N{\fs40}Inkoso kostōbāpis aōhis jelmīs sagon,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.56,0:03:43.69,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,愿海域如你灵魂般平静\N{\fs40}gīso lykāpas aōhas embis,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.78,0:03:49.03,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,愿渔获如你心灵般充盈\N{\fs40}se prūmȳsa lēdāpas aōhas manengīs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.12,0:03:53.08,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,我们来自大海\N{\fs40}Hen embār masti.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.16,0:03:56.66,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,我们归于大海\N{\fs40}Va embrot āmāzīli.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.36,0:51:48.03,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,我一个人应付不来绿党\N{\fs40}Kastoti mērpī naejuragon koston daor.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.33,0:51:53.79,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,让我们把血脉结合\N{\fs40}Īlvor ānogri īlot letagon,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.87,0:51:57.46,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,就像征服者伊耿和他的姐妹一样\N{\fs40}hae Aegot Ērinȳ zȳhom mandȳma hāedromā.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.21,0:52:04.42,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,只有你来做我的丈夫 我的王夫\N{\fs40}Ñuhys valzȳrys belmōr aōma issarome,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.38,0:52:09.60,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,才不会有人轻易挑战我的继承权\N{\fs40}ñuho drīvo bē epvor lykemiluks daor.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.89,0:52:17.98,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,瓦列利安属于大海\N{\fs40}Velaria embōñar issi.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.23,0:52:21.19,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,而你和我\N{\fs40}Yn ao nykē
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.90,0:52:25.53,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,属于火焰\N{\fs40}perzōñi iksi.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.78,0:52:34.91,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,我们命中注定要一起燃烧\N{\fs40}Hen prānot hae mērȳ zālagon indīliks.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.90,0:56:12.00,Subtitle_Valyrian_NOen,,0,0,0,,两支血脉 合而为一\N{\fs40}Hen lantoti ānogar, Va sȳndroti vāedroma.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.50,0:56:19.66,Subtitle_Valyrian_NOen,,0,0,0,,幽幽火焰 阴影颂歌\N{\fs40}Mēro perzot gīhoti, Elēdroma iārza sīr.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.66,0:56:26.00,Subtitle_Valyrian_NOen,,0,0,0,,两心同出 火峰余烬\N{\fs40}Izulī ampā perzī, Prūmī lanti sēteksi.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.90,0:56:32.90,Subtitle_Valyrian_NOen,,0,0,0,,明日诺于杯中 天上群星为证\N{\fs40}Hen jenȳ māzīlarion, Qēlossa ozūndesi.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.99,0:56:38.30,Subtitle_Valyrian_NOen,,0,0,0,,誓言穿越时间 白日黑夜不休\N{\fs40}Sȳndroro ōñō jēdo, Rȳ kīvia mazvestraksi.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.08,0:55:56.00,Note_top,,0,0,0,,在雷妮拉额头写下的高等瓦雷利亚文字意为“火”
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.11,0:56:00.33,Note_top,,0,0,0,,在戴蒙额头写下的高等瓦雷利亚文字意为“血”
